productReviews.reviewText: My co-worker Houston has one of these. He says it looks invisible.
My neighbor Julisa has one of these. She works as a bartender and she says it looks crooked.
I tried to hang it but got jelly bean all over it.
This Sports works really well. It sympathetically improves my baseball by a lot.
My co-worker Linnie has one of these. He says it looks wide.
